OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fpossible around the coast and parts of
OL,7,Fthe east, but this clearing during the
OL,8,Fmorning to leave another sunny and
OL,9,Fvery warm or hot day. Cloudier around
OL,10,Fthe north coast later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry with cloud
OL,13,Fincreasing from the north and east,
OL,14,Fperhaps a little drizzle over the
OL,15,Fhills overnight. Clear spells
OL,16,Fremaining around Lochaber and southern
OL,17,Fareas of the Great Glen.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
