OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMost of the cloud thinning and
OL,6,Fclearing during the morning with
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells. Feeling warm
OL,8,Fin the sunshine, but remaining cooler
OL,9,Fand cloudier near the north coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and settled, although a little
OL,13,Fearly light rain or drizzle possible
OL,14,Fover the hills. Rather cloudy, but
OL,15,Fbright or sunny spells developing.
OL,16,FFeeling warm in any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
